                                        <td align="left" style="padding-top: 5px;" width="20%">
                                            <strong>Date</strong>
                                        </td>
                                        <td align="left" width="10%">
                                            <strong>:</strong>
                                        </td>
                                        <td align="left" style="padding-top: 5px;padding-left: 10px;" width="70%">
                                            <span t-field="doc.offer_date"
                                                  t-options="{&quot;widget&quot;: &quot;date&quot;}"/>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr style="width: 100%;">
                                        <td align="left" style="padding-top: 5px;">
                                            <strong>To</strong>
                                        </td>
                                        <td align="left">
                                            <strong>:</strong>
                                        </td>
                                        <td align="left" style="padding-top: 5px;">
                                            <span t-field="doc.partner_id.name"/>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </td>
                            <td width="70%" valign="top" align="right">
                                <h2 class="mt16">
                                    <span>Offer No#</span>
                                    <span t-field="doc.name"/>
                                </h2>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td width="50%" valign="top" align="left">
                                <u>Offer letter / رسالة عرض</u>
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                <span>We thank you for the interest shown in leasing the subject property we are pleased
                                    to offer you based on the following details
                                </span>

                            </td>
                            <td width="50%" valign="top" align="right" style="padding-left: 25px;">
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                <span>شكركم على اهتمامكم باستئجار الوحدة, و يسعدنا عرضنها عليكم  حسب التفاصيل التاليه:</span>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td width="100%" colspan="2" valign="top" align="left">
                                <br/>
                                <u>
                                    <b>Unit breakdown / تفاصيل الوحدة</b>
                                </u>
                            </td>

                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    <table style="border: 1px solid black;border-collapse: collapse;width: 100%;page-break-inside: avoid;font-size: 14px;">

                        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;border-collapse: collapse;width: 100%;">
                            <td class="text-left" width="50%"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                Property<br/>العقار
                            </td>
                            <td class="text-left" width="50%"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                <span t-field="doc.unit_id.property_id.name"/>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;border-collapse: collapse;width: 100%;">
                            <td class="text-left"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                Apartment / Villa<br/>شقة / فيلا
                            </td>
                            <td class="text-left"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                <span t-field="doc.unit_id.name"/>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;border-collapse: collapse;width: 100%;">
                            <td class="text-left"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                Size (Sq. Ft)<br/>الحجم (قدم مربع)
                            </td>
                            <td class="text-left"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                <span t-field="doc.unit_id.sq_ft"/>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;border-collapse: collapse;width: 100%;">
                            <td class="text-left"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                Annual Rent<br/>الايجارالسنوي
                            </td>
                            <td class="text-left"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                AED &amp;nbsp;
                                <span t-field="doc.total_rent"/>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;border-collapse: collapse;width: 100%;">
                            <td class="text-left"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                Contract Period<br/>مــــدة العقــــــد
                            </td>
                            <!-- <t t-foreach="doc.unit_line_ids" t-as="line"> -->
                            <td class="text-left"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                <span t-esc="contract_period"/>
                            </td>
                            <!-- </t> -->
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;border-collapse: collapse;width: 100%;">
                            <td class="text-left"
                                style="padding:5px;padding-left: 25px;border-left: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black;">
                                Security Deposit<br/>قيمة التأمين
                            </td>
